thread.title: Peter

author: Peter
title: Peter
text: Nik at Nelson Alexander is the best in the business. I have dealt with heaps of agents in the past and the responsiveness and professionalism of Nik is always outstanding. I have referred 2 other contacts who also use Nik and Nelson Alexander for their property management needs and they have all voiced the same opinion to me. Well done Nik and the Nelson Alexander team
